"""{{SOR_DISPLAY_NAME}} — SGNL custom polling adapter (Python).

Implements ``sgnl.adapter.v1.Adapter.GetPage`` using grpcio. Generated by
.cursor/skills/sgnl-sor.

Env:
    SGNL_ADAPTER_VALID_TOKENS  Comma-separated shared secrets SGNL sends
                               in the gRPC ``token`` metadata. Required.
    SGNL_ADAPTER_PORT          Listen port (default 8081).
    SGNL_ADAPTER_SOR_TYPE      If set, GetPage enforces datasource.type match.

Build the proto stubs once:
    python -m grpc_tools.protoc -I. --python_out=. --grpc_python_out=. adapter.proto

Entities (external_id → upstream endpoint):
{{ENTITY_ROUTE_COMMENT}}
